The paper deals with the performance analysis of uplink transmission in a massive MIMO system, which involves channel estimation, linear and nonlinear receivers, energy savings, and training optimization. These topics are closely related to information theory (cs.IT), networked systems (cs.NI), control and optimization (cs.SY), signal processing (cs.MM), and communication (cs.COM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, in descending order of relevance.
